author: BuyLowSellNever
body:

body: Thanks a lot. I’ve got a few of those, including Qcom, on my watchlist and will defo buy when i feel we are closer to the bottom. In terms of intel i just personally dislike how poor they have been in terms of integrated graphics & just think they haven’t be pushing enough

author: BuyLowSellNever
body:
QCOM is honestly one of the best stocks you can buy.


Massively undervalued with, great management team and strong long term growth potential.


Their quite highly leveraged though, so if you’re happy with that than I vote buy buy buy.


Definitely in my top 3 stocks to own!
